title: The International Bad Boys Hour Ep 56: Smoothie Punch Cards with Feng Chao!
description: Welcome to another exciting episode of The International Bad Boys Hour!  Sam and Steve are back in the studio with guns a blazing!  Sam discusses his MTV taping and Steve goes off about never selling out to the man.  The International Bad Boys then welcome Comedy Store legend Feng Chao to the show.  Feng talk about getting white chicks pregnant, Russian hookers, 3rd shift monsters and he has some serious words for the Palmers!  All of this and more on latest International Bad Boys Hour!  Thank you so much for listening and please let us know what you think.  Listen, Learn Rate and Review!!! Thank you for your support!
